ЄIn Memory of Bill and Dulcie O'Leary
Died Aged 84 and 87
Loving Mum and Dad
Gran and Grandad
Great Gran and Grandad
Great Great Gran and Grandad
We love and miss you both"Н
КWith fondest memories of our dear Father, Sister & Mother

BILL GILES
1906-1986
Amongst so much else, Dad was once a Scout Leader here at Holy
Trinity Church, a school-teacher & a driving instuctor. Born with
a wanderlust, he came home to his roots to relish his closing years.

MAUREEN GANT
1938-2002
A gifted musician & home-maker, a music teacher & choir-leader,
Maureen lived locally all her life, but was taken from us before her time.

MURIEL GILES
nГ©e Selifant
1912 - 2008
Born at Aldon, Ninesprings was both her playground & pathway to school.
After their wanderings, Mum & Dad returned to Yeovil to enjoy retirement until Maureen's early demise took Mum away to her final home in Surrey."г
